---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Safety & Responsibility | C-Mind">
  <div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-teal-600">Core Values</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Safety & Responsibility</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
          Safety and responsible use are foundational to the design of C-Mind. The platform is not a replacement for professional mental health care, diagnosis, or treatment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
        <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
          
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
              <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-600 text-2xl text-white">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
              Built-in Safeguards
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              <p class="flex-auto">C-Mind incorporates safeguards intended to identify situations where additional human or clinical support may be needed, including escalation pathways for crisis or high-risk scenarios.</p>
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
              <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-600 text-2xl text-white">‚öñÔ∏è</span>
              Ethical & Responsible AI
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              <p class="flex-auto">The platform is developed with attention to ethical AI principles, data protection, and appropriate use within healthcare and research environments.</p>
            </dd>
          </div>

        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>